---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Retail - Leaders In Incentives, Rewards & Loyalty Programs | GRG India"
  description="Run Incentive Programs for Retailers, Distributors & Sales Associates. Craft and execute incentive programs that fuel revenue growth with GRG India."
  ogImage="https://www.grgindia.in/images/solutions/retail-hero.png"
>

  <!-- ==================== HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="bg-[#f5f5f8] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#0f1f3d] anim-fade-up">
            Run Incentive Programs for Retailers, Distributors & Sales Associates
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-[#4a5568] anim-fade-up" data-anim-delay="100">
            Whether you're overseeing retail outlets, distribution channels, or sales teams, our solution equips you to craft and execute incentive programs that fuel revenue growth.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 anim-fade-up" data-anim-delay="200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Elevate store performance</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Cash & digital rewards</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">End salesperson analytics</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Inspire distribution and channel partners</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.g2.com/products/my-incentives/reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow anim-fade-up" data-anim-delay="300">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5">
              <span class="text-[#FF492C] text-xl">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span><span class="text-[#FF492C] text-xl opacity-50">&#9733;</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Read our reviews on</span>
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#FF492C"/>
              <text x="12" y="28" fill="white" font-size="22" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif">G</text>
              <text x="24" y="22" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif">2</text>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/solutions/retail-hero.png" alt="Retail incentive programs for store associates and distributors" class="w-full h-auto anim-slide-right" data-anim-delay="200" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== TESTIMONIALS ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-[#0f1f3d] anim-fade-up">Enabling Companies Just Like You</h2>
      <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 anim-fade-up flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-gray-600 italic leading-relaxed flex-1">
            "My Incentives helped us build long-term relationships with 8,000+ carpenters pivotal in lock sales. The app-based program features barcode scanning for instant rewards, self-registration with KYC workflows, and gamification through milestone campaigns — delivering validated sales data and a direct relationship with influencers."
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <img src="/images/logos/godrej.png" alt="Godrej" class="h-10 object-contain mx-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 anim-fade-up flex flex-col" data-anim-delay="100">
          <p class="text-gray-600 italic leading-relaxed flex-1">
            "My Incentives powers our multi-audience program across internal sales, general trade and EBO outlets. Retail shop-boys submit invoice screenshots for last-mile visibility, while auto-calculated incentives and gamification — quizzes, leaderboards, target meters — drive engagement across our 1,000+ team."
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <img src="/images/logos/damensch.jpg" alt="DaMensch" class="h-10 object-contain mx-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== REUSED: 3 PRODUCT FEATURES ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#f8f8f8]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-20">

        <!-- Automate Calculations — text left, image right -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="px-2 md:px-6 anim-fade-up">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d]">Automate Calculations & Approvals</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              Access a flexible rule engine for complex incentive calculations. Configure approval workflows for instant payouts, and track every aspect of these programs from a single platform.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">No-code rule builder (IF / THEN / ELSE)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Configurable approval workflows</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Instant payout calculation with full audit trail</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/my-incentives/automate-calculations.png" alt="Rule engine with IF/THEN/ELSE logic" class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto anim-fade-in" data-anim-delay="100" />
        </div>

        <!-- Drive Performance — image left, text right -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <img src="/images/my-incentives/drive-transparency.png" alt="Target meter and earnings tracker" class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto order-2 md:order-1 anim-fade-in" data-anim-delay="100" />
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2 px-2 md:px-6 anim-fade-up">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d]">Drive Performance with Transparency</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              Create multiple incentive programs for as many target groups as you wish. Give your sales teams and channel partners real-time visibility into their targets, achievement, and earnings — driving motivation through transparency.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Real-time target meters & progress tracking</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Automated WhatsApp/SMS nudges</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Live earnings dashboard for participants</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Payout & Compliance — text left, image right -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="px-2 md:px-6 anim-fade-up">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d]">Payout and Compliance Automation</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              Drive compliant, low-error rate payouts for users, at scale. Support UPI, NEFT, Amazon Gift Cards, PhonePe and more — with built-in KYC verification including PAN card, GST, and bank details.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Multiple payout methods (UPI, NEFT, gift cards)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Built-in document verification & KYC</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#E41E3A] shrink-0"></span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">GST-compliant with full audit trails</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/my-incentives/payout-compliance.png" alt="Payment methods and document verification" class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto anim-fade-in" data-anim-delay="100" />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== CTA ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] anim-fade-up">Ready to Transform Your Retail Incentive Programs?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto anim-fade-up" data-anim-delay="100">
        See how My Incentives can help retailers, distributors and sales associates drive real results.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/book-a-demo/"
        class="mt-8 inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#E41E3A] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b8162e] transition-colors anim-fade-up"
        data-anim-delay="200"
      >
        Book a Demo
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
